      <title>土耳其媒体赛前煽动狂热情绪，德国向球迷发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/euro-2024-german-police-warns-turkish-fans-ahead-of-class-with-netherlands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于德国警方向球迷发出警告，且土耳其媒体煽动民族主义热情，周六晚举行的 2024 年欧洲杯四分之一决赛土耳其与荷兰之间的比赛有可能成为一场导火索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/euro-2024-german-police-warns-turkish-fans-ahead-of-class-with-netherlands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 13:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
