      <title>TotalEnergies 考虑降低部分客户的油价上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/totalenergies-considers-lower-pump-price-cap-for-some-customers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TotalEnergies SE 首席执行官 Patrick Pouyanne 表示，该公司正在考虑降低其法国服务站针对订购该公司电力和天然气服务的驾车者的价格上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/totalenergies-considers-lower-pump-price-cap-for-some-customers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 12:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
